snippet.title: Orb Of The Watcher First Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Orb Of The Watcher today!

A tribute to the old adventure games of the nineties. Orb Of The Watcher is party based RPG where you explore the tunnels under a large city to find a magical artifact. Encountering friends, enemies and the odd pile of gold along the way.

"Morgana Rides " Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
